To install clone repository to your home dir. Create symlinks

Installed plugins and how to use them

closetag
Use C-_ to close a nearest open tag. Work in HTML & XML

Spellchecking
Enable spell checking by hitting F5. Navigate to next misspelt word by ]s or [s
to move backwards. Use z= to get a list of suggestions.

In Insert mode, when the cursor is after a badly spelled word, you can use
CTRL-X s to find suggestions. This works like Insert mode completion. Use
CTRL-N to use the next suggestion, CTRL-P to go back.

